title: Mathematics-Quick Review Formula Sheet
description:
This is a very useful and handy formula sheet made by me for people who are struggling to remember important formulas. It covers the following function and equation theories found below:

-Linear & Non-Linear Equations
-Supply & Demand Equations
-National Income Determination
-Profit Analysis & Marginal Functions
-Homogeneous Functions
-Logarithm Functions
-Percentages
-Compound Interest
-Savings & Annuity
-Investment Appraisal
-Elasticity
-Properties Of Derivatives
-Definite/Indefinite Integrals

Note: I have got an A Grade on my course for "Mathematics For Economics & Business", so you can rely on the information provided with full confidence. Injoy !!!!
